              <p class="project-type">
                Finished builds with a clear final result, physical prototype, or tested outcome.
              </p>

              <div class="trait-list">
                <span>DeckStep™</span>
                <span>Combat Robot</span>
                <span>Electric Guitar</span>
                <span>Ride-On Mods</span>
