              <h3 class="card-title">3D Models</h3>
              <p class="project-type">
                CAD models, assemblies, mechanisms, design studies, and class-based modeling work.
              </p>

              <div class="trait-list">
                <span>Fusion 360</span>
                <span>Creo</span>
                <span>Assemblies</span>
                <span>GD&T</span>
