              <div class="timeline-content">
                <p class="timeline-date">May 2026 – Present</p>
                <h3>Motorola Solutions</h3>
                <p class="timeline-role">Battery Cell Engineering Intern</p>

                <ul>
                  <li class="typewrite">Supporting lithium-ion cell safety testing using thermal, vibration, shock, microscopy, and electrical test equipment.</li>
                  <li class="typewrite">Evaluating cell performance, charging behavior, and safety response for battery characterization and compliance testing.</li>
                  <li class="typewrite">Working under senior electrical and mechanical engineers on product reliability and safety problems.</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="trait-list">
                  <span>Battery Systems</span>
                  <span>Cell Testing</span>
                  <span>Thermal Chambers</span>
                  <span>Vibration Testing</span>
                  <span>Safety</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
