            <div class="timeline-card">
              <div class="timeline-media">
                <img src="/images/experience/TipTek_Logo.png" alt="TipTek logo" />
              </div>

              <div class="timeline-content">
                <p class="timeline-date">October 2025 – January 2026</p>
                <h3>Tiptek, LLC</h3>
                <p class="timeline-role">Laboratory Technician</p>

                <ul>
                  <li class="typewrite">Manufactured and aligned 90+ tungsten nanoprobes per shift using precision tools for semiconductor failure analysis.</li>
                  <li class="typewrite">Performed optical and digital inspection to verify nanoprobe geometry and tip radius at sub-10 nanometer scale.</li>
                  <li class="typewrite">Worked in a precision lab environment requiring consistency, accuracy, and careful microscope-based inspection.</li>
