                  <li class="typewrite">Trained and mentored 8+ employees in safety procedures, customer service, and technical services.</li>
                  <li class="typewrite">Provided hardware solutions for 50–70 customers per shift while managing inventory and special orders across 2000+ SKUs.</li>
                  <li class="typewrite">Handled key duplication, paint matching, screen repairs, and cutting/rethreading pipe.</li>
